  'q_al_alabama-gdl-restrictions-daily-life_0', 'quiz_al_alabama-gdl-restrictions-daily-life', 'During what hours is a Stage I Restricted License holder generally prohibited from driving in Alabama?', '["10:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m.","11:00 p.m. to 6:00 a.m.","Midnight to 6:00 a.m.","Midnight to 5:00 a.m."]', 2, 'Alabama''s GDL prohibits Stage I drivers from operating a vehicle between midnight and 6:00 a.m., with limited exceptions for work, school, religious, medical, and hunting/fishing trips, or when accompanied by a qualifying adult.', 0
