  'q_ar_arkansas-gdl-restrictions-in-daily-life_0', 'quiz_ar_arkansas-gdl-restrictions-in-daily-life', 'What are the nighttime driving curfew hours for an Arkansas Intermediate License holder?', '["9:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m.","10:00 p.m. to 6:00 a.m.","11:00 p.m. to 4:00 a.m.","Midnight to 5:00 a.m."]', 2, 'Arkansas prohibits Intermediate License holders from driving between 11:00 p.m. and 4:00 a.m., except for work, school activities, or when accompanied by a licensed driver 21 or older.', 0
