  'q_az_az-gdl-restrictions-daily-life_0', 'quiz_az_az-gdl-restrictions-daily-life', 'During the first 6 months of a Class G license, what are Arizona''s nighttime curfew hours for teen drivers?', '["10:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m.","11:00 p.m. to 6:00 a.m.","Midnight (12:00 a.m.) to 5:00 a.m.","There is no nighttime restriction in Arizona"]', 2, 'Arizona''s teen curfew runs from midnight to 5:00 a.m. — narrower and later than most states. Exceptions exist for work, school, religious activities, emergencies, or driving with a parent/guardian.', 0
