- and 17-year-olds.","needsReview":["Exact minimum license age in decimal form (16 years 4 months -> 16.333)","Whether 8-hour ''safe driving practices'' course counts toward classroom hours when completed via secondary school route","Current fine amounts for GDL violations (subject to legislative change)","Whether parent training requirement is 2 hours in all current statutes","Latest cell phone enforcement penalties as of 2026"]}}', unixepoch('now')*1000, 'Generated; school must review and tweak.', unixepoch('now')*1000
