  'q_ct_ct-gdl-restrictions-daily-life_1', 'quiz_ct_ct-gdl-restrictions-daily-life', 'What is Connecticut''s nighttime driving curfew for first-year teen drivers?', '["10:00 PM to 4:00 AM","11:00 PM to 5:00 AM","Midnight to 6:00 AM","9:00 PM to 6:00 AM"]', 1, 'Connecticut prohibits driving between 11:00 PM and 5:00 AM during the first year, with limited exceptions for work, school, religious activities, and medical needs.', 1
