  'q_de_delaware-rules-and-quirks_0', 'quiz_de_delaware-rules-and-quirks', 'Under Delaware''s Move Over Law, what must you do when approaching a stopped emergency vehicle with flashing lights?', '["Maintain speed and stay in your lane","Change lanes away if safe, otherwise slow to a reasonable speed below the posted limit","Stop completely until the emergency vehicle leaves","Honk to acknowledge the responder"]', 1, 'Delaware''s Move Over Law requires changing lanes away from the stopped emergency vehicle when safe; if you cannot change lanes, you must slow to a reasonable speed below the posted limit.', 0
