  'q_ga_georgia-specific-rules-and-quirks_0', 'quiz_ga_georgia-specific-rules-and-quirks', 'Joshua''s Law requires applicants under age 17 to complete how many hours of classroom instruction and supervised driving?', '["20 classroom + 30 driving, 4 at night","30 classroom + 40 driving, 6 at night","40 classroom + 50 driving, 10 at night","15 classroom + 25 driving, 3 at night"]', 1, 'Joshua''s Law requires 30 hours of classroom driver education plus 40 hours of supervised driving (at least 6 at night), certified on Form DS-1.', 0
