  'cp_mi_teen_overlay', 'mi-teen-overlay', 'Michigan Teen Overlay', 'state', 'US-MI', 'Michigan-specific supplement covering the three-step Graduated Driver Licensing program administered by the Secretary of State: how to earn a Level 1 Temporary Instruction Permit through Segment 1 driver education, how Level 2 restrictions on nighttime driving and teen passengers shape daily life, and Michigan-specific rules including the 2023 hands-free law, Segment 2 requirements, and the path to a full Level 3 license at 17.', unixepoch('now')*1000
);
