  'q_mi_how-to-get-a-permit-in-michigan_0', 'quiz_mi_how-to-get-a-permit-in-michigan', 'What is the minimum age to apply for a Level 1 Temporary Instruction Permit in Michigan?', '["14 years 0 months","14 years 9 months","15 years 0 months","16 years 0 months"]', 1, 'Michigan requires applicants to be at least 14 years 9 months old and to have completed Segment 1 driver education before being eligible for a Level 1 permit.', 0
