tal/guardian consent is required for any applicant under 18.","needsReview":["Exact required supervised practice hours (50 commonly cited; verify NDDOT current requirement)","Whether BTW hours are formally mandated at 6 versus recommended by curriculum providers","Current exact wording of nighttime restriction window for under-16 restricted license","Whether instruction permit holders have any explicit passenger limit beyond supervising driver requirement","Latest NDDOT fee schedule for permit and license issuance"]}}', unixepoch('now')*1000, 'Generated; school must review and tweak.', unixepoch('now')*1000
);
