  'q_nh_how-to-get-licensed-in-new-hampshire_3', 'quiz_nh_how-to-get-licensed-in-new-hampshire', 'How many hours of supervised practice driving must a NH teen complete before licensing?', '["20 hours, with 5 at night","30 hours, with 6 at night","40 hours, with 10 at night","50 hours, with 15 at night"]', 2, 'New Hampshire requires 40 hours of parent-supervised practice driving, with at least 10 of those hours after dark.', 3
