 a specific logged practice hour total like many states; verify whether to record 0 or leave null)","Whether the 6 classroom hours figure should reflect the driving-school theory component or the broader high school driver education curriculum","Decal fee amount and current cost ($4 per pair as of last known update)","Exact statutory citation for Kyleigh''s Law passenger and curfew exceptions for religious observance"]}}', unixepoch('now')*1000, 'Generated; school must review and tweak.', unixepoch('now')*1000
