  'q_nj_how-to-get-a-nj-permit_0', 'quiz_nj_how-to-get-a-nj-permit', 'At what age can a New Jersey teen first obtain a Special Learner''s Permit through a licensed driving school?', '["15","15 and a half","16","17"]', 2, 'The Special Learner''s Permit is available starting at age 16, but only through a licensed New Jersey driving school — not directly at the MVC.', 0
