  'q_ok_oklahoma-gdl-restrictions-daily-life_2', 'quiz_ok_oklahoma-gdl-restrictions-daily-life', 'Under Oklahoma''s intermediate license passenger rule, which scenario is legal?', '["Driving three non-family friends to practice","Driving your sister and one friend to a game","Driving four classmates home from school","Driving two friends home at 11 PM"]', 1, 'Family members do not count toward the one non-family passenger limit, so a sibling plus one friend is allowed.', 2
