her the 100-hour practice requirement without driver ed is still current under latest ODOT rules","Confirm cell phone rule citation (ORS 811.507) wording for under-18 drivers","Confirm provisional license passenger restriction excludes ''immediate family'' vs. ''members of the driver''s immediate family''"]}}', unixepoch('now')*1000, 'Generated; school must review and tweak.', unixepoch('now')*1000
