  'q_pa_how-to-get-a-pa-learners-permit_1', 'quiz_pa_how-to-get-a-pa-learners-permit', 'How many hours of supervised practice driving must a Pennsylvania applicant under 18 complete before the road test?', '["40 hours","50 hours","65 hours","80 hours"]', 2, 'PA requires 65 supervised hours, including 10 at night and 5 in inclement weather, certified on Form DL-180C.', 1
