  'q_ri_rhode-island-specific-rules-and-quirks_0', 'quiz_ri_rhode-island-specific-rules-and-quirks', 'When entering a Rhode Island rotary (roundabout), who has the right of way?', '["The vehicle entering the rotary","The larger vehicle","Vehicles already traveling within the rotary","Whoever signals first"]', 2, 'Drivers entering a rotary must yield to vehicles already circulating inside it.', 0
