  'q_tx_tx-ittd-and-quirks_0', 'quiz_tx_tx-ittd-and-quirks', 'How close to a teen''s driving skills test must the Impact Texas Teen Drivers (ITTD) video be completed?', '["Within 30 days before the test","Within 90 days before the test","Within 6 months before the test","Any time before the test, with no expiration"]', 1, 'ITTD completion is valid for 90 days. If you took it more than 90 days before your skills test, you''ll need to retake it.', 0
