  'q_ut_utah-specific-rules-and-quirks_0', 'quiz_ut_utah-specific-rules-and-quirks', 'What is the adult per-se DUI blood alcohol limit in Utah?', '[".02",".05",".08",".10"]', 1, 'Utah lowered its adult per-se DUI limit to .05 BAC — the strictest in the nation.', 0
