  'q_vt_vermont-gdl-restrictions-daily-life_1', 'quiz_vt_vermont-gdl-restrictions-daily-life', 'Vermont''s nighttime restriction for junior operators applies during which hours?', '["Midnight to 5 a.m.","10 p.m. to 6 a.m.","Sunset to sunrise","9 p.m. to 5 a.m."]', 2, 'Vermont uses ''sunset to sunrise'' rather than fixed clock hours, which is especially significant in winter when sunset comes early.', 1
