ying for a probationary license. Sponsorship by a parent or guardian is required for applicants under 18.","needsReview":["Exact minimum permit age (15 years 6 months) — confirm against current WisDOT GDL chart","Whether the 30 supervised hours / 10 night hours requirement has changed in recent rule updates","Whether ''qualified adult'' definition (21+, licensed 2+ years, or parent/guardian/spouse 19+) is still current","Most current cell phone statute citation and any 2024+ amendments","Whether probationary nighttime restriction end time is 5:00 a.m. statewide or varies"]}}', unixepoch('now')*1000, 'Generated; school must review and tweak.', unixepoch('now')*1000
);
