  'q_wv_wv-gdl-restrictions-daily-life_0', 'quiz_wv_wv-gdl-restrictions-daily-life', 'During which hours are West Virginia Level 2 drivers generally prohibited from driving unsupervised?', '["9:00 p.m. to 6:00 a.m.","10:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m.","11:00 p.m. to 4:00 a.m.","Midnight to 6:00 a.m."]', 1, 'The WV nighttime restriction for Level 2 runs from 10:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m., with limited exceptions for work, school, religious, and emergency travel.', 0
