  'q_wv_wv-specific-rules-and-quirks_0', 'quiz_wv_wv-specific-rules-and-quirks', 'On a narrow West Virginia mountain road where two vehicles cannot pass, which driver should yield?', '["The uphill driver always yields","The downhill driver yields to the uphill driver","The larger vehicle always yields","Neither — both must back up equally"]', 1, 'The downhill driver yields because the uphill driver has less control and a harder restart on a grade.', 0
