  'q_wy_how-to-get-a-wyoming-learner-permit_0', 'quiz_wy_how-to-get-a-wyoming-learner-permit', 'What is the minimum age to apply for a standard Wyoming Learner Permit?', '["14","15","16","17"]', 1, 'Wyoming allows teens to apply for a standard Learner Permit beginning at age 15. A separate restricted rural permit may be available earlier for agricultural families.', 0
